    "Walia and Kapoor [35] introduced a general survey on tracking using multiple modality data in 2016.",
    "Baltrusaitis et al. [38] provided a detailed review of machine learning methods using multi-modal information.Various differences and developmental approaches are observed even among the most related works [35,40].",
